A security analyst discovers a web application processing XML input that includes the following DTD declaration:
```xml
&lt;!DOCTYPE foo [ &lt;!ENTITY xxe SYSTEM &quot;file:///etc/passwd&quot; &gt; ]&gt;
&lt;search&gt;&lt;term&gt;cosa&lt;/term&gt;&lt;/search&gt;
```
Which PICERL phase is the team most likely in, and what is the immediate priority action?

